    dc:description "Figs.1–4. Jezekia kmenti sp.nov. 1–3 –J paratype:1 – abdominal sternites 3 to 5; 2 – cerci and surstyli; 3 – pregonites and epiphallus. 4 – ♀ paratype, abdominal sternites 5 to 8. Scale bars: 0.5 mm (Figs. 1–2, 4), 0.1 mm (Fig. 3)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5319123/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

